attributes.name: Pulsar Terp Slurper Twist Set
attributes.body:
Banger not included

Terp Pearls (also referred to as terp beads) are a popular type of dabbing accessory that look like small beads made of quartz or borosilicate glass. Add a couple of terp pearls inside your banger bucket during your dab session to spin and spread your concentrates for bigger clouds and tastier terp flavor. The spinner style is made to create a vortex of air inside the bucket that will get your terp pearls spinning. You can also use any carb cap that is made to direct airflow and position it so that your terp pearls start spinning. 

For those dabbers who want to take it to the next lever, adding terp pearls to your setup is the answer. The spinning beads will provide you with huge hits that are super tasty. If you are into low-temp dabs the pearls will also help you achieve this.

attributes.name: Cannavis Syrup - Mango 300mg
attributes.body:
This syrup is a delicious addition to your favorite beverages and recipes. Crafted with a commitment to quality, Cannavis is proud to be sugar-free, gluten-free, and vegan-friendly, making it suitable for a wide range of dietary preferences.

Its fast-acting formula allows you to enjoy its effects by simply placing a drop under your tongue or mixing it with your preferred beverage.

But that's not all - it's also an excellent ingredient for cooking and baking. Cannavis opens up a world of creative possibilities for cannabis enthusiasts and culinary enthusiasts alike.

attributes.name: Og Inc - Blueberry Pancake - 1g Live Resin
attributes.body: Live Resin is a unique form of concentrate in that the flower used is frozen immediately after harvest, rather than the typical process of curing. Freezing the raw cannabis flower helps preserve terpene and cannabinoid profiles, providing consumers with a robust flavor profile and precise effects.

attributes.body: Shatter is a form of concentrate that is made by extracting cannabinoids and terpenes from cured cannabis flower. Shatter is translucent and stable at room temperature, but can range in consistency from very brittle to having a "pull-n-snap" quality.

attributes.body: The full spectrum refers to the full spectrum of cannabinoids found inside the oil. Cannabis oil is usually very thick, dark, and is taken at precise amounts.
